    (IsIntegralClosure.algebraMap_injective S R L)] at h
  exact isUnramifiedAt_of_Separable_minpoly' K L p hpbot (IsIntegralClosure.mk' S x hx)
    (by rwa [IsIntegralClosure.algebraMap_mk']) h
